Requires:

+ Snort 3 installation
+ LightSPD installation

-------------------------------------------------
Edit these files:

setup.sh - configure for your environment.
test.sh - the configs and pcaps you want to test.
common.lua - set appropriate thread pinning

-------------------------------------------------
Then do this:

$ ./run.sh <mode> <cpu#> <policy> <pcap>

Output is to terminal.

To get help:

$ ./run.sh

-------------------------------------------------
Or run everything:

$ ./test.sh <mpse>

Output is in logs/<mpse>_<policy>_<pcap>.log

-------------------------------------------------

